fields.value: Census of population and housing, 1970 urban atlas tract boundaries

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This file contains latitude-longitude (decimal degrees) descriptions of boundaries of 1970 Standard Metropolitan Statistical Area's census tracts. The boundary data are presented in the form of polygons with common boundaries repeated for each polygon. Islands with holes internal to polygons are treated as separate polygons.

SMSA and tract number within SMSA are identified on each record.

The coordinates for the boundaries of the census tracts within SMSA's pertain to their defini tion as of 1970

publicationCitation.value: Urban Atlas GE80- (number of report) (name of SMSA), Washington: U.S. Government Printing Office.
